{"tid":669925,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"筲箕灣街頭老婆斬傷老公　報警自首","createTime":"2018-05-19T01:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T06:14:11.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8cce5c72ef240cdc195ab856a8195eb0408f3366","tid":669925,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T01:48:43.000Z","msg":"筲箕灣望隆街發生倫常血案，早上7時23分，警方接報指一名男子在筲箕灣港鐵站對出遭一名女子用刀斬傷後腦及後頸，救護員趕至，為他包紮後送院治理，懷疑涉案的妻子一度逃去，約半小時後自行到筲箕灣道28號筲箕灣報案中心自首。警員在港鐵B1出口對開的垃圾桶檢獲一把菜刀，正調查事主遇襲原因。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，女事主為家庭主婦，其60餘歲丈夫在街市賣菜，近日丈夫疑另結新歡，兩夫婦正辦理離婚手續。事發時，兩夫婦正與丈夫現任女友同行，<span style=\"color: red;\">期間女事主涉嫌從自己的手袋內取出菜刀</span>，斬傷丈夫。<br />\n<br />\n帶刀侍衛黎架?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-NpW8Vwjj8NI/WiunQH3LDMI/AAAAAAAA1w8/-_QxDgGIc20JzUhMLUft0qR6tw4pjwc1QCHMYCw/w700/151281025_753_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-NpW8Vwjj8NI%2FWiunQH3LDMI%2FAAAAAAAA1w8%2F-_QxDgGIc20JzUhMLUft0qR6tw4pjwc1QCHMYCw%2Fw700%2F151281025_753_0.jpg&h=20187757&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d648291bee38fb83de025b0ef37d16876f31283a","tid":669925,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T01:49:53.000Z","msg":"又仁王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9443d36562ae50a03f72ba90647611cbf502e3","tid":669925,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d648291bee38fb83de025b0ef37d16876f31283a","tid":669925,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T01:49:53.000Z","msg":"又仁王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T01:51:19.000Z","msg":"仲有無玩<br />\n見你玩MHW 多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00041ed54ba0d045e75800b0d74e8259b313050","tid":669925,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T01:51:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8f2